API SPEC

/me - POST
  - creates a user returns
    {token, user}

    if the user name is already taken returns
    {success:false, message:}


/signin - POST
  -post { username: , password: }
  -returns jwt if successful

  if creditentials inccorect
  {success:false, message:}

all need JWT token in Header as
Authorization: 'Bearer '+token

/me - GET
  -returns user
  {user}

/me - PUT
  -pass in fields you want to update
  -returns updated user
  {user}

-me - DELETE
  -returns deleted user
  {user}